<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><sub><strong>&#171;</strong> <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/aiad-homescreen">HUB</a> | <span style="color: blue">Part I: ALERT! LOCKDOWN INITIATED!</span> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/command-query-separation">Part II</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/superencipherment">Part III</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/clock-multiplier">Part IV</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/null-terminating-string">Part V</a> <strong>&#187;</strong></sub></p>
</div>
