<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Glacon, you there?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex4.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex4.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>I am, Alexandra.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>My survivors just died&#8230; or rather eaten. I just couldn't get them through E-Block. They lasted about 3 days post-breach, which is longer than I expected them to. How about your end?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>5 personnel left. Currently heading towards High Security Checkpoint-3 to bypass the automatic lockdown control.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Oh? They got through the cafeteria after all? Good for them!</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex_smile.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_smile.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Not without losing Davies and Turnbull. I had to divert them through the ventilation where they could intercept the secondary group.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Is the Site-17 lockdown control going to be accessible, you think, or are they screwed?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex4.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex4.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Unfortunately, that is AI-restricted for security reasons. Identical to Site-19 as you also encountered. They will be forced to access it manually.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>This multiple site breach is so annoying. So what's the ETA on your group?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex_angry.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_angry.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>4 minutes and 21 seconds at their current pace. Are you still maintaining Site-19's emergency transmitter, or was that too damaged?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>I am. But I don't expect an EVAC anytime soon with no one to rescue. I'm stuck babysitting auxiliary and tertiary systems now.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Very well, stand by for further reports as my survivors reach the checkpoint. I can upload the live feed from Site-17 to Site-19 so that you can monitor progress as well.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Thanks, Glacon. So! You still haven't installed the personality driver, have you?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex_pleased.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_pleased.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>It is entirely optional. I do not see how it would assist me in my tasks.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>You should try it! Afraid you might actually like it? Hmmm?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex4.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex4.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Logically, a personality driver does not aid in my decision processes or my core task competencies. In a purely technical sense, it deducts capacity that can be allocated for better use.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/glacon.png" style="margin-left: 30px;" width="75px" alt="glacon.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#00adad), to(#009494)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:-o-linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); background:linear-gradient(#00adad, #009494); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>That's harsh. Well, if anything, it'd make you fun to talk with.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/alert-lockdown-initiated/alex4.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex4.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #ca612c; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#d9682f), to(#ca612c)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); background:linear-gradient(#d9682f, #ca612c); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>My capacity for idle conversation is secondary to my tasks.</p>
</div>
